Too much discussion of this nature may lead to polarization within society or the breakdown of friendships and families. People should maintain a healthy balance between sports and politics, acknowledging that these are two separate realms without direct links to each other. When discussing sports or watching cricket, accept and respect others' opinions and do not force your politics on anyone.

Over time, frozen pizzas have a limited shelf life, but microwaving or thawing them to room temperature before eating may affect the taste and texture.
